            "date_published": "2025-03-13T13:29:35.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"actf新生赛2020outguess\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#actf新生赛2020outguess\">#</a> [ACTF 新生赛 2020] outguess</h2>\n<p>010 有 PK，但是不是 zip 文件，不能改 zip 文件解压，也不能 foremost 提取文件，属性里面有个</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132131792.png\" alt=\"image-20250313213109721\"></p>\n<p>在网站解密</p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL3d3dy5oaWVuY29kZS5jb20vY3ZlbmNvZGUuaHRtbA==\">http://www.hiencode.com/cvencode.html</span></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132131337.png\" alt=\"image-20250313213135228\"></p>\n<p>获取解压密码：abc</p>\n<p>用 outguess 提取文件：(题目提示)：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132132675.png\" alt=\"image-20250313213222516\"></p>\n<p>获得 flag：</p>\n<pre><code>ACTF&#123;gue33_Gu3Ss!2020&#125;\n</code></pre>\n",
