            "title": "梅花香自苦寒来",
            "date_published": "2025-03-13T12:14:08.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"梅花香自苦寒来\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#梅花香自苦寒来\">#</a> 梅花香自苦寒来</h2>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132015425.png\" alt=\"image-20250313201524372\"></p>\n<p>给了这个东西直接 010 看一下，没有 PK，没有隐藏 zip 文件</p>\n<p>但是是 jpg 文件以 FF D8 开头，FF D9 结尾</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132016418.png\" alt=\"image-20250313201647362\"></p>\n<p>后面还有好多字符</p>\n<p>将这些十六进制字符转换一下换成这样：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132110147.png\" alt=\"image-20250313211033087\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132110207.png\" alt=\"image-20250313211022001\"></p>\n<p>扫描二维码就好了</p>\n",
