            "title": "谁赢了比赛？",
            "date_published": "2025-03-13T11:56:17.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"谁赢了比赛\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#谁赢了比赛\">#</a> 谁赢了比赛？</h2>\n<p>一张图片，拖入 010 看是不是隐藏了 zip 文件</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132001817.png\" alt=\"image-20250313200053710\"></p>\n<p>果然有，直接随波逐流解码文件</p>\n<p>archpr 爆破 1020：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132001479.png\" alt=\"image-20250313200119443\"></p>\n<p>两个文件</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132002312.png\" alt=\"image-20250313200201272\"></p>\n<p>flag.txt 没有 flag</p>\n<p>就只有 hehe.gif 这个图片了</p>\n<p>用 stegslove 这个软件：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132004587.png\" alt=\"image-20250313200455543\"></p>\n<p>有这一帧</p>\n<p>保存下来：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zty--666.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/202503132006847.png\" alt=\"image-20250313200610785\"></p>\n<p>下面的 save</p>\n<p>在 Red plane 0 获取一个二维码扫一下就有了</p>\n<pre><code>flag&#123;shanxiajingwu_won_the_game&#125;\n</code></pre>\n",
